    <p class="text-[16px] text-[#57534e] leading-[1.75] mb-4">We built this because every existing option had at least one of three problems: paid-only ($300+/mo), email-gated, or didn&apos;t apply industry compliance rules. Here&apos;s how we compare:</p>
